msgstr "Efek tetap"

msgid "Random effects"
msgstr "Efek acak"

msgid "Ordered effects"
msgstr "Efek terurut"

msgid ""
"%1$s and %2$s are the group-level effect size and standard deviation, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"%1$s dan %2$s adalah ukuran efek tingkat grup dan deviasi standar, masing-"
"masing."

msgid "%s is the group-level effect size."
msgstr "%s adalah ukuran efek tingkat grup."

msgid "Bayes factor of the random effects H%1$s over the fixed effects H%1$s."
msgstr "Faktor Bayes dari efek acak H%1$s di atas efek tetap H%1$s."

msgid ""
"Posterior estimates are based on the models that assume an effect to be "
"present. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: fixed effects H%2$s & "
"random effects H%2$s over the fixed effects H%1$s & random effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi posterior berdasarkan model yang mengasumsikan efek untuk "
"ditampilkan. Faktor Bayes berdasarkan semua empat model: efek tetap H%2$s & "
"efek acak H%2$s di atas efek tetap H%1$s & efek acak H%1$s."

msgid ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates for %3$s are not yet available, but will "
"be added in the future. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: random "
"effects H%1$s & H%2$s over the fixed effects H%1$s & H%2$s."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi posterior direrata model untuk %3$s belum tersedia, tetapi akan "
"ditambahkan di masa depan. Faktor Bayes berdasarkan semua empat model: efek "
"acak H%1$s & H%2$s di atas efek tetap H%1$s & H%2$s."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the (unconstrained/constrained) random effects H%1$s over "
"the fixed effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"Faktor Bayes dari efek acak (tidak terbatas/terbatas) H%1$s di atas efek "
"tetap H%1$s."

msgid "Bayes factor of the fixed effects H%1$s over the random effects H%1$s."
msgstr "Faktor Bayes dari efek tetap H%1$s di atas efek acak H%1$s."

msgid ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates are based on the models that assume an "
"effect to be present. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: fixed "
"effects H%1$s & random effects H%1$s over the fixed effects H%2$s & random "
"effects H%2$s."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi posterior direrata model berdasarkan model yang mengasumsikan efek "
"untuk ditampilkan. Faktor Bayes berdasarkan semua empat model: efek tetap "
"H%1$s & efek acak H%1$s di atas eefek tetap H%2$s & efek acak H%2$s."

msgid ""
"Model averaged posterior estimates for %3$s are not yet available, but will "
"be added in the future. The Bayes factor is based on all four models: fixed "
"effects H%1$s & H%2$s over the random effects H%1$s & H%2$s."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi posterior direrata model untuk %3$s belum tersedia, tetapi akan "
"ditambahkan di masa depan. Faktor Bayes berdasarkan semua empat model: efek "
"tetap H%1$s & H%2$s di atas efek acak H%1$s & H%2$s."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the fixed effects H%1$s over the (unconstrained/constrained) "
"random effects H%1$s."
msgstr ""
"Faktor Bayes dari efek tetap H%1$s di atas efek acak (tidak terbatas/"
"terbatas) H%1$s."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the ordered effects H%1$s over the fixed effects H%2$s. The "
"Bayes factor for the ordered effects H%1$s versus the unconstrained (random) "
"effects H%1$s model is %3$.3f."
msgstr ""
"Faktor Bayes dari efek terurut H%1$s di atas efek tetap H%2$s. Faktor Bayes "
"untuk model efek terurut H%1$s versus efek (acak) tidak terbatas H%1$s "
"adalah %3$.3f."

msgid ""
"Bayes factor of the fixed effects H%2$s over the ordered effects H%1$s. The "
"Bayes factor for the unconstrained (random) effects H%1$s versus the ordered "
"effects H%1$s model is %3$.3f."
msgstr ""
"Faktor Bayes dari efek tetap H%2$s di atas efek terurut H%1$s. Faktor Bayes "
"untuk model efek (acak) tidak terbatas H%1$s versus efek terurut H%1$s "
"adalah %3$.3f."

